headline: Coinbase Institutional Says Several Signs Point To 'Crypto Winter' But Remains Optimistic About H2 2025
summary: Coinbase Institutional has suggested that the cryptocurrency market is at the start of a bearish cycle. Bitcoin and major altcoins have fallen below a key technical level. Coinbase Institutional does not expect the cryptocurrency bear market cycle to last long. Amid declining prices and growing market uncertainty over the past few months, the burning question on the minds of several cryptocurrency market participants has been: Is the bull market cycle over? headline: Coinbase in hot water over $12 million ‘content coin’—but exec tells haters to lean in
summary: Detractors said the U.S. crypto exchange was buying into memecoin mania. Pollak says he was just having fun "on chain.”
